---
title: Mexican Spiced Stew with Black Beans and Sweetcorn
description: Our chef Mimi recently returned from Mexico, having energetically scaled Mayan pyramids and wandered around ancient sites. Whilst admiring these wonders, she stumbled upon a street vendor supplying the locals with a spicy black bean and sweetcorn stew. Truly inspired, our intrepid explorer returned and created this delectable dish to tickle your taste buds!
